            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary" style="">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            后续！“和副市长平级”的公职人员殴打湖北老板，官方：批评教育          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">纪人物</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                纪人物              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">纪人物</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">renwujjj</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">记录最真实的人物，记住每个人物的精彩！</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true"></span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-track="1" style='margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>近日，一则“公职人员殴打酒店老板”的信息那可谓疯狂网络，引发多方关注，这三位可以说凭一己之力给公职人员的队伍抹黑啊！</p><p><img data-imgfileid="100062754" data-ratio="0.387037037037037" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKBI7VlicGH8JOGcLLd7nlPTibm9ZlSIYQiarPgic637tib6EhicGldTQMLzPlw/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="other" data-w="1080" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: auto;cursor: zoom-in;display: block;border-radius: 4px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><br></p><p data-track="2" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>据悉事情发生在2月15日湖北襄阳，<span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ; ">襄阳市一名公职人员与他的朋友们一同前往枣阳市的一家酒店，他们选择了一个房间，打算在其中享受打牌的乐趣。然而，没过多久，</span>他们嫌弃酒店环境不好，很吵闹，陈某于是要求退房，并退钱，当时老板觉得他们没打多久，理应把钱退给他们。</p><p data-track="3" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ; ">尽管酒店老板内心有些不情愿，但他仍然选择了息事宁人，将钱款如数退还给了他们。随后，公职人员与他的朋友们便离开了酒店。</span></p><p><img data-imgfileid="100062752" data-ratio="0.7805555555555556" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKBqrF1xPxWs443IgQjJUOQ8USts1aJd7iaUN4nYI92GVNEb6Qp0DApF7w/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="other" data-w="720" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: auto;cursor: zoom-in;display: block;border-radius: 4px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><br></p><p data-track="4" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>可是让老板万万没想到的是，没过一会儿他们又回来啦，称是老板没退给他们钱，他们身上的钱数不对，要求老板再次退钱。</p><p data-track="5" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ; ">老板疑惑地表示，难道那笔款项已经退回？然而，张某却坚定地否认了这一点。</span></p><p data-track="6" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ; ">为了揭开真相，老板提议查看相关视频记录，一切自会水落石出。然而，张某却嫌麻烦，催促老板尽快退款，希望能尽快离开这个地方。面对张某的催促，老板选择了沉默，转身去帮助一位刚刚抵达的客人办理住房登记。</span></p><p><img data-imgfileid="100062751" data-ratio="0.7791666666666667" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKBpJo2Vo2odIRhiaaC2wGX4TdfH9lopczynOh096yvichiaibia5HBccXppMQ/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="other" data-w="720" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;ma